original_title: Clubhouse Detectives in Search of a Lost Princess
overview: In this Clubhouse Detectives flick four kids stumble upon a plot to kidnap a lost princess hidden in their very town. They start investigating all of the girls in school to find out which girl is the lost princess so they can protect her from the villain who is out to make her disappear. Will they find the princess in time?
title: Clubhouse Detectives in Search of a Lost Princess
